flowchart LR
    U[Users / Apps] --> A[API Gateway]
    A --> O[Agent Orchestrator\nLambda or ECS Fargate]
    O --> DA[Direct answer\nSynchronous HTTP response]
    O --> RR[Response Router\nReturn final answer to user]

    O --> M[Amazon Bedrock\nLLM + Guardrails]
    O --> W[AWS Step Functions\nMulti-step workflow]
    O --> T[Tool Executors\nLambda Functions]
    T --> I[Enterprise Systems\nRDS / SaaS / Internal APIs]

    O --> R[Memory & Retrieval]
    R --> D[DynamoDB\nSession memory]
    R --> S[S3 clinical documents\nGuidelines / policies]
    R --> KB[Bedrock Knowledge Base\nRAG control plane]
    S --> INGEST[Ingestion flow\nChunk + embed documents]
    INGEST --> EMB[Titan Embeddings\nCreate vectors]
    EMB --> OSS[OpenSearch Serverless\nVector Store]
    KB --> OSS

    O --> RET[Query flow\nRetrieve top passages]
    RET --> KB
    OSS --> RET
    RET --> CTX[Inject retrieved context\ninto system prompt]
    CTX --> M

    O --> E[Event Layer\nEventBridge + SQS/SNS]
    E --> EB[EventBridge Bus\nhealthcare-agent-bus]
    EB --> ES1[auth_denied\nWAF block + alarm + SNS]
    EB --> ES2[request_invalid\nrate-limit + DDoS monitor]
    EB --> ES3[policy_denied\nSIEM + compliance queue]
    EB --> ES4[guardrail_blocked\nsafety metrics + retrain]
    EB --> ES5[human_review_requested\nHITL FIFO + SLA watchdog]
    EB --> ES6[human_review_rejected\nescalation + audit log]
    EB --> ES7[invoke_success\nusage analytics + billing]

    ES5 --> SQ1[HITL Review Queue.fifo\nReviewer Lambda + task token]
    ES3 --> SQ2[Compliance Queue\nAudit writer Lambda]
    ES4 --> SQ3[Safety Review Queue\nSafety analyst Lambda]
    ES7 --> SQ4[Audit Ingestion Queue\nHIPAA audit writer]

    SQ1 --> SF1[AWS Step Functions\nHITL Review Workflow\nStandard]
    SF1 --> WF[WaitForCallback\n72h task token]
    WF --> DEC[Decision?]
    DEC -->|approved| HR[Human answer / approval]
    DEC -->|rejected| BAD[AuditAndEnd]
    HR --> RR

    SQ2 --> SF2[AWS Step Functions\nCompliance Workflow\nStandard]
    SQ3 --> SF3[AWS Step Functions\nSafety Review Workflow\nStandard]
    SQ4 --> SF4[AWS Step Functions\nIngestion Workflow\nExpress]
    SF4 --> MAP[Map state\nParallel chunk embedding]

    DA --> RR
    M --> RR
    W --> RR
    T --> RR
    BAD --> SAFE[Safe refusal / escalation reply]
    SAFE --> RR
    MAP --> RR
    RR --> U

    O --> C1[CloudWatch Logs]
    O --> C2[CloudWatch Metrics/Alarms]
    O --> C3[X-Ray Tracing]

    A --> G5[WAF + Shield]
    O --> G1[IAM Roles]
    O --> G2[KMS Encryption]
    O --> G3[Secrets Manager]
    O --> G4[CloudTrail Audit]

